---
title: One-Pot Char Siu Pork Meatball & Noodle Soup with Green Beans
description: A fragrant noodle soup is exactly what you need in the cooler months to warm you up from the inside out. Pork meatballs,
infused with ginger and lemongrass, simmer in a flavour-packed broth with golden egg noodles and tender veggies. You’ll be slurping your way to happiness in no time!
